{"tid":1848351,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"微信發言「寧疫情死千人不願Kobe離世」　江蘇男被拘留7天","createTime":"2020-01-28T12:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T18:58:32.000Z","uid":10199,"like":365,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":109,"replies":[{"pid":"5b6745b958b1379f54d61acc0c3c2a5058134755","tid":1848351,"uid":10199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3t4x4u4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3t4x4u4.png&h=0cbc8c29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國近日武漢肺炎疫情持續擴大，而昨（27）日又傳出美國籃壇湖人傳奇巨星Kobe（Kobe Bryant），發生墜機意外身亡事件，有1名中國網友表示，寧願疫情擴散，也不希望Kobe離世，目前他已經被當地警方拘留。<br />\n <br />\n根據中國《澎湃》網站消息，這名江蘇徐州的網友「剛子」，在《微信》群內發言說：「寧願看到疫情擴散，死上千人，也不願看到科比（Kobe）離開世上的消息」。<br />\n <br />\n這個發言馬上被群內的1名友人反嗆：「你說的這個屁話」，但沒想到的是，「剛子」的發言也被當地警方掌握，當天就被徐州警局以「涉嫌尋釁滋事」的罪名，處以「行政拘留7日」。<br />\n <br />\n中國網友紛紛留言表示：「抓得好」、「絕對是黑粉」、「告訴大家個好消息，這貨被（工作）單位開除了」、「這事科比如果知道，他肯定不會承認你是他的球迷」。"},{"pid":"22c73ca92dbbdec75e6fdac0d0c88d3017c0dfbc","tid":1848351,"uid":76310,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:02:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fappeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGVtn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=003799cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china</a><br />\n要求香港真雙普選作為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢度簽得七七八八<br />\n麻煩fb tg發出去搵新客源簽"},{"pid":"eed1b8315b45916f9ea01f9ed56080e26c28a69b","tid":1848351,"uid":38904,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:03:22.000Z","msg":"反正支那人命就是賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkg